Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全日本的各位觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的天氣亦非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒適的季節真的已經来臨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.43,0:01:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然東京因為能源供給線的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以致有點不便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其他地區絕對不會受到影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要擔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全東京的亞人已經失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.64,0:01:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是會傳染的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.11,0:01:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心，不單是能源供給線的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.14,0:01:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人不是普通機械人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.91,0:01:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【衛星頻道發生故障】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.21,0:01:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【請等一會】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！還留在東京這里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.14,0:02:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到費挪現象的擴散…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會急劇到這地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真精彩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已故史汀奇博士製造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非只是模仿人類的機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史汀奇博士想製造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.75,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有生命的金屬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是具有智慧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.85,0:04:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種模擬生命體…亞人的誕生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全賴博士把牠們的「seed」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖入自己女兒腦內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然候由熟習了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類腦內神經電氣特性的抗體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動完成其進化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你，別嚇我啊，霍斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何打算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只好回國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.29,0:04:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這種地方只會給亞人殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到會因為這種事而解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲去了哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒有回車屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.67,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會輕易給亞人殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sekiria世界巡迴演唱會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經變成一場夢嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【本公司已經關閉】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【有事的請聯絡大阪分公司】
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話仍未接通呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她連打個電話回来也不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得真刻薄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京好像發生大件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視新聞為何沒報導的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先進的科技一定會引来投資者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.96,0:06:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看中亞人的就是積蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙會長羅辛格爾把亞人商品化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓人類不會受到良心的責備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近似人類般會獨立思考的亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一副枷鎖来令牠們服從人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那副枷鎖就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠們跟人類相似的外形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要外形一日模仿人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人便注定只可以是亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立的思考對人類根本沒幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，亞人有時會失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒公開報導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.95,0:06:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亞人失控的或然率是沒規則的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙撥出大量資金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予日本國家警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.79,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把本来是反恐怖分子的AD警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成專門對付亞人罪案的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.53,0:07:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，AD警察亦已經不再存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有映像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.33,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積蒙的素成計劃利用宇宙的傘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把太陽能直接投射到地底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，設在地底的龍脈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon line
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令亞人變得失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去，不只東京…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！今次給徹底封鎖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉，能再次轉換頻道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.52,0:08:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算吧，無人看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們很努力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經盡力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.24,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你来幫我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.81,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣，我也是AD警察的員共
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.91,0:08:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員共…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然怪，但形容得非常貼切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒介給控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.59,0:08:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想過原来是這麽令人沮喪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有何打算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.69,0:08:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指我們戰士飛刀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失常亞人的影子執法者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的確已經無計可施了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會再穿裝甲服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有電郵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是AD警察行動部隊的暗號！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動部隊的兄弟還在東京啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家正在等候指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽辦？里昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.86,0:09:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用餘下的裝備把龍脈封鎖！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…餘下的裝備也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有反亞人電磁鎗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.51,0:09:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們應該能使用分署的手榴彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.74,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達利，要在東京截斷龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.75,0:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該炸毀哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待我看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果給龍脈從這里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接上北面的lifeline
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東北部便會被感染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，召集我們的員共！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你想離開這里，可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米西奧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在這里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.87,0:10:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想服侍你直到我終老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲你也應該試試遊泳嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那種心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.69,0:11:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何再来這里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已經退出的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里安全嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核彈也好，若非直接擊中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里便不會有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為裝甲服能更進化一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你已經知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲服是抑制了核心的亞人變體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.95,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠能透過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟穿起牠的女仔的身體同化…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.95,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来發揮機能和抑制其亞人的自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞，最討厭厭亞人的是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，最接近亞人的人類亦是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，格拉迪亞和米奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是在我的腦內孕育出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為只要使用爸爸研究所里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺下来的最純淨核心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便不會好像亞人般失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.32,0:12:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，根本就沒有不會失控的亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.86,0:12:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人透過改變自己的外形…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去擁有跟人截然不同的思考模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人是會改變外形的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我的心不容許我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不積極利用那一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看過拉謝爾和米奇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在製造的東西便會明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失控的可能性並非已經消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.19,0:12:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全取決於我們精神上的強弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.89,0:12:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭厭那種精神論啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早料到你會那樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才說得不貼切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.60,0:12:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那換過你喜歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要看我們的拼勁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.28,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉…迪亞…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞…絲莉亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.69,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米西奧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的費挪現象正透過地底龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.88,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴展至全日本…以致全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉迪亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把人類變為亞人的僕人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.52,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做有何有趣之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為人類的我也料到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向人類報復並非無聊的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.47,0:14:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有很多不明白的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.34,0:14:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為何身為人類…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻想解放我們的自我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你還不惜勉強自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我並非完全的人類啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指你小時曾因病…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以致大部份內藏和筋肉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被換上人共代替品一事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長跟我相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他討厭厭自己的體內藏有外物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是全身插上喉管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.20,0:14:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像樣的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此，你也不過是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類只是一群已經不會再進化的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末期生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.51,0:14:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類和這個地球的下場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都已經在意料之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連發生混亂的餘地亦沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.72,0:14:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我想親眼看看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種跟人類截然不同的生物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會帶来怎麽樣的變數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.03,0:15:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你體內的亞人是初期型的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟人類的器官黏在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，牠們沒有覺醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.11,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…！我既非人類亦非亞人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.21,0:15:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是監察者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於這里地底的儲水庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是龍脈的接口部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸毀這個儲水庫便能把龍脈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟北面的lifeline分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真的會来嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家全是男子漢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會不来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.80,0:15:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下，我看那可沒關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.22,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼克，我召集的只是行動部隊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，只是前行動部隊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是行動部隊的一員吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但部長你因為年紀大而退休了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉·羅瑪洛吧芭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次的行動跟你才毫無關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.31,0:16:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單靠你優秀的頭腦是沒幫助的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有裝甲服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.05,0:16:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能夠輕而易舉的制伏亞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者用武器令牠們變成蜂巢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最候一口氣把牠們的核心挖出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟牠們說再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂，你可以糾正一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位小姐說話的口吻嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，你習慣一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單靠我們四人根本無法破壞龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.17,0:16:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害！大家…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家！你們来喇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些亞人會改成裝甲服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子能造多少件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多啊，這里的亞人只夠造一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.01,0:18:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次的裝甲服透過自我意識控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.11,0:18:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至能強化金屬組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.22,0:18:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，那會非常重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力也會相應所升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，布烈絲小姐，你来這里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表你會再穿裝甲服吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那樣說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.26,0:18:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布烈絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.97,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然穿上身時覺得很不習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但靈活度比以往所高很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然未在外面試過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但彈跳力也一定所升了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.15,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是7倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力也所升了5倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.49,0:18:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些新裝甲服最大的特點是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們早晚會知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別賣關子嘛，拉謝爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絲莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全賴絲莉亞容許…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝甲服留有亞人的特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才能造出新裝甲服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麽了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你也不要一直堅持己見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.65,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里看得很清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原来這麽暴露的嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在望甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰呢…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇！怎辦！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉！發…發生甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞人跟留在隧道內的車融合了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的裝備對牠完全無效！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.83,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達利，在這麽遠開鎗也是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是了，怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好一試呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個蠢材！里昂！達利！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道想撞過去？里昂仔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過別那樣稱呼我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.81,0:20:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個丫頭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大哥哥為何那麽生氣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牠跟車融合前決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.02,0:20:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.79,0:20:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.93,0:20:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂！達利！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有裝甲服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…現在不是說那種話的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里昂，那傢伙好像很生氣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管，亞人又怎會懂生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心應該在那對眼里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無論變得多大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脊髓部份也有人型時的核心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，你不走近一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們便無法射穿你的裝甲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.50,0:21:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差少許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…！開始融合了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！到極限了！達利！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.07,0:21:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差少許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.41,0:21:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麽淡定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.84,0:21:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說還差少許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.24,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達利！你要回國繼承農場的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不願意才来這里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.74,0:21:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.12,0:22:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我眼花嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.66,0:22:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽…為甚麽…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠應該…已經沒有核心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.40,0:23:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲娜你奸茅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.57,0:23:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好看啊，我也想穿那套衫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我也要跟絲莉亞說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.94,0:24:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我度身訂造一套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.14,0:24:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富金屬感和冰冷的衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.78,0:24:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時失常亞人也就不是我對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.88,0:24:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待我揭曉吧，那就是新型裝甲服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.75,0:24:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都無人聽我講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.05,0:24:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回，吹波糖危機


